{
  "stem": "11904.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You were talking about the friend that you met on the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was her name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Sara Gibstayn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I saw her, I can't express the reaction what I had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, here I was from such a fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, knowing that your whole family and everybody around you is dead-- and there, I find a friend.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we couldn't really show anything that we know each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were afraid that, you know, they'll think something-- they'll wonder where?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were sort of staying apart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I knew that she was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was a great, great relief for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did she end up being in the same place?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same city.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, in another place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was still '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still the fall, '42.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was sent in another place to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was in this place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, we had Sundays off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we visited, once in a while, each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I'm telling-- I think I couldn't have survived all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she gave me, and I gave her, strength.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And to be able to have somebody that close, and to be able to talk to, was-- that's exactly what we needed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because to keep a secret like that in you, you know, that nothing happened, when so much happened, it was not an easy thing to do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I stayed with this family for-- till Christmas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This friend, Sara-- now she's-- can I say what they call her now?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call her Sonya Fox.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She got married, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she has children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She lives in Albuquerque, New Mexico.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she knew about another friend that did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was in-- in Austria.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
